<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV9">
<l>tātulāvu koṉṟaimālai tuṉṉuceñca ṭaiccivaṉ</l>
<l>nītiyālva ṇaṅkupāta niṉmalāni lāyacīr</l>
<l>vētavāṇar kītavēḷvi nītiyāṉa kēḷviyār</l>
<l>nītiyāl vaṇaṅkukiṉṟa nīrmainiṉka ṇiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O [Lord] whose feet are worshipped according to the rules</l>
<l rend="indent">by Śiva with red, thick matted locks</l>
<l rend="indent">who [wears] garlands of laburnum pervaded by pollen!</l>
<l>O blemishless [Lord]! Rests in You the nature of being worshipped</l>
<l>by the [Brahmans] whose occupation [is to recite] the Vedas</l>
<l rend="indent">with pervading excellence</l>
<l>[and] by those whose learning is based on sacrifices [full of Sāmavedic] chantings.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
